tt1192628.title: Rango
tt1192628.writer: John Logan, Gore Verbinski, James Ward Byrkit
tt1192628.actors: Johnny Depp, Isla Fisher, Timothy Olyphant
tt1192628.plot: Rango is an ordinary chameleon who accidentally winds up in the town of Dirt, a lawless outpost in the Wild West in desperate need of a new sheriff.
